  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Life in nature</h2>Will an ordinary city dweller be able to cope with nature? You will have to start living with a clean slate and settle down in a new place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/8ef4080afb0a4c6e50a92304339a0e07.poster.avif?t=1696314333\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/8ef4080afb0a4c6e50a92304339a0e07.webm?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/8ef4080afb0a4c6e50a92304339a0e07.mp4?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your own farm</h2>Get resources and build up your farm.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/b51d466ac3d7d51621f7cd910f09766d.poster.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/b51d466ac3d7d51621f7cd910f09766d.webm?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/b51d466ac3d7d51621f7cd910f09766d.mp4?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Neighbours</h2>Locals will help you settle down in a new place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/76b5f436f745b7c524b99f644d21eea6.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure</h2>Explore dangerous places and fight monsters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/527d7de8d2422dbc20427b9b30be3f24.poster.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/527d7de8d2422dbc20427b9b30be3f24.webm?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/527d7de8d2422dbc20427b9b30be3f24.mp4?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fishing</h2>Relax with fishing. Go to the river or sea with a fishing rod. You can catch a wide variety of fish and more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/df61011e955deab28723d56814314bec.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Animal husbandry</h2>Animals are very useful in the farm. Get yourself animals and don't forget to take care of them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/480a8e63e0d64deab6fd072374e04eeb.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=244 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Garden</h2>Also do not forget to look after plants and flowers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/65e66eb2c9c3b10357a7b410caeb6655.poster.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/65e66eb2c9c3b10357a7b410caeb6655.webm?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/65e66eb2c9c3b10357a7b410caeb6655.mp4?t=1696314333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cooking</h2>Cook various meals. As a person leading an active lifestyle and protecting the farm from monsters, it is important for you to eat well.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518770/extras/561a7d86258cb4941f8e227ca6ec03c5.avif?t=1696314333\" width=600 height=88 /></span>",
